---
title: Hoisin Beef Noodles with Toasted Sesame Seeds
description: Sweet-savoury hoisin sauce is the star of this speedy wonder! Twirl beef, stir-fried veggies and toasted sesame seeds into fresh chow mein noodles, all tossed in that delicious sauce, for an unforgettable dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hoisin-beef-noodles-ebb6dac3.jpg
